FT  01 JUL 93 / UK Company News: Ferromet
In 1992 Ferromet Group reduced its losses before tax from Pounds 12.9m to
Pounds 1.14m. And extraordinary credits of Pounds 8.99m turned that into an
overall profit of Pounds 7.84m.
Turnover came to Pounds 1.88m.
The loss arises from administration expenses, a substantial part of which
related to restructuring.
Losses per share were 0.56p (6.27p).
